snippet.title: BOSSGARD reveal trailer
snippet.description: WHO’S THE BOSS? Well, it’s finally you! So grab your friends and get ready for the craziest fights in our fast-paced asymmetrical multiplayer game. Choose between a variety of unique BOSSES, brave vikings and WHACKY arenas, grab a gamepad or a smartphone and remember: the more the merrier!
